snippet.title: Best VGM 71 - Donkey Kong Country 2 - Stickerbush Symphony (Bramble Blast)
snippet.description:
Stickerbush Symphony, but Very Slow: https://youtu.be/O0-tThDmHAg
My remix: http://youtube.com/watch?v=Sqa2yctcAEM

See also:

Best VGM 470 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITQVlvGsSDA
Best VGM 606 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYOdCD4mWsk
Best VGM 718 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZgvsIvHJTds
Best VGM 1150 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RSm22cu707w
Best VGM 1804 - https://youtu.be/PGowEQXyi3Y

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Donkey Kong Country 2
Stickerbush Symphony (Brambles in the Breeze / Bramble Blast)
